{"tid":1296717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"40市民「暢遊」屯門公園　街坊斥：曾遇長者打量13歲女兒","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:40:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8be99658d505b176485a7c866a79c1634f365319","tid":1296717,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/2f06cf6be03c2e7ac60f309bcd111bd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F2f06cf6be03c2e7ac60f309bcd111bd0.jpg&h=30d0e621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/2d5387869d72d4f90021b12a58253f77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F2d5387869d72d4f90021b12a58253f77.jpg&h=38b214c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190708/s00001/2d802bccee0380ab7184d117b6b78130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F2d802bccee0380ab7184d117b6b78130.jpg&h=f2f19a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有市民發起今午（8日）「暢遊屯門公園」行動，約40人參與，希望行使投訴權利，要求康文署就噪音問題執法。行動期間，公園內不見「大媽」放聲高歌場面。發起人形容，10多年來未試過如此寧靜，期望康文署完善執法規例，讓市民有公平使用公園的權利。<br />\n<br />\n行動發起人甄先生表示，在屯門居住逾30年，近3年來受屯門公園噪音、大媽唱歌等問題滋擾，情況加劇，使用場地的權利亦受影響。<br />\n<br />\n甄先生期望康文署外判保安員就製造噪音的「大媽」執法；立法會就此修例，讓康文署管理人員可擔當證人處理噪音投訴。他說，擔心日後噪音問題會持續，未來會繼續在網上發起後續行動，約一個星期一次。<br />\n<br />\n屯門街坊張太表示，前日（6日）曾與13歲女兒到屯門公園遊行，惟沿途有男長者「色迷迷」打量女兒說「呢條肥妹仔OK喎」，令女兒感到害怕及不願再到公園。張太認為，現時公園充斥大媽，已經「變質」。<br />\n<br />\n行動期間，有中年女子批評參與者擾亂公園秩序和沒禮貌，有參與者向她遞上一個紅色利市封，該女子用手推開，有人指她打人，要求警方執法。雙方擾攘約10分鐘後，有警員到場帶該女子上警車離開，稱會帶她往警署。該女子眼泛淚光、表現驚慌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190708/s00001/1562584976059/40%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e3%80%8c%e6%9a%a2%e9%81%8a%e3%80%8d%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e5%85%ac%e5%9c%92-%e8%a1%97%e5%9d%8a%e6%96%a5-%e6%9b%be%e9%81%87%e9%95%b7%e8%80%85%e6%89%93%e9%87%8f13%e6%ad%b2%e5%a5%b3%e5%85%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562584976059%2F40%25e5%25b8%2582%25e6%25b0%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%259a%25a2%25e9%2581%258a%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%259c%2592-%25e8%25a1%2597%25e5%259d%258a%25e6%2596%25a5-%25e6%259b%25be%25e9%2581%2587%25e9%2595%25b7%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%2589%2593%25e9%2587%258f13%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%2585%2592&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpQFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=6cb39341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190708%2Fs00001%2F1562584976059%2F40%25e5%25b8%2582%25e6%25b0%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%259a%25a2%25e9%2581%258a%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%259c%2592-%25e8%25a1%2597%25e5%259d%258a%25e6%2596%25a5-%25e6%259b%25be%25e9%2581%2587%25e9%2595%25b7%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%2589%2593%25e9%2587%258f13%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%2585%2592&h=53429e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190708/s00001/1562584976059/40%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e3%80%8c%e6%9a%a2%e9%81%8a%e3%80%8d%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e5%85%ac%e5%9c%92-%e8%a1%97%e5%9d%8a%e6%96%a5-%e6%9b%be%e9%81%87%e9%95%b7%e8%80%85%e6%89%93%e9%87%8f13%e6%ad%b2%e5%a5%b3%e5%85%92</a>"}]}